    },
    {
      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "Pick the right amount of intelligence",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Latency is not just infrastructure. It is the shape of the promise you make to the user.</p>"
        },
